    "The attention gate model described in Fig. 10 was first introduced by Oktay et al.",
    "Sang et al.",
    "introduce AG-CUResNeSt, a unique neural network architecture that improves Coupled UNets with enhanced techniques for integrating skip connections and attention gates (Sang et al. 2021).",
    "To suppress the redundant low-level information from the encoders, attention gates are implemented into skip connections within each UNet.",
    "To achieve high accuracy in polyp segmentation, the network is capable of efficiently merging multilevel characteristics and utilizing semantic information flow."
